title: 【#生スバル】ウマ娘 プリティーダービーやるしゅばああああああああああああああああああああああああああああああ！！！！！！！！：Umamusume: Pretty Derby【ホロライブ/大空スバル】
name: Oozora Subaru

entries.text: I have a quick question before we start.
Is this "Race" something I should watch with everyone?
Like, the button is right there.
I guess I'll show it for a sec.
Yeah, I should probably show it.
Haaah! Shuba-shuba-shuba! Hololive's Oozora Subaru here! Good evening!
So, today, we're playing *Uma Musume Pretty Derby*!
I'm going to play for the first time in a while.
Oozora Subaru has played this once before.
Ah, crap, the romaji input is on!
Yeah... I couldn't win at all.
I want to win a little bit.
I want to get started, but— ah, wait a sec.
It's not showing up on screen.
Uma Musume experts, the Hololive experts,
taught me everything from A to Z.
plentiful, so I should be fine.
Like, apparently I can win now.
I still can't do it even now?
Gonna close it for a sec.
I'm going to play the Steam version.
This is a huge tangent, but...
I had a toothache at the exact same time.
Maybe Uma Musume and Subaru's teeth
I was playing Uma Musume while gritting my teeth.
that Uma Musume isn't being recognized.
It was showing up just a moment ago.
Can you wait just a sec?
Like, the capture is acting weird.
It's that thing where it says 80%, right?
so I'll close it once, sorry.
Ah, but the download is mostly done, so...
Can everyone hear me right now?
hear me now, it might be that.

OBS stopped moving and I was like,
I might have made it quite low.
so I did a radio commentary broadcast!
You want it higher? I'll raise this.
Ah, then I'll raise this one.
Alright, I am a rookie Trainer.
I remember you! I remember you!
You were there when I opened the door

"I am honored to meet a promising rookie Trainer like you."

"A race where Uma Musume compete, loved by people all over the world."
"The dream stage you aim for with your assigned Uma Musume."
"It is the fanfare for the start of the race."
Wait, I saw up to here earlier.
What are these triangles and stuff?
I understand! I understand Uma Musume!
I understand everything about Uma Musume!
I saw this in the anime!
"Popularity is shown by Double Circle, Circle, Triangle."
Eh, why are there three of them?
Does that mean they run three times?

"Waiting for the start is this Uma Musume..."
"She is the Uma Musume I expect the most from."

"For Uma Musume, the Winning Live is..."

Can I listen at full volume?

Hey, Tazuna-san! The afterglow! The afterglow!
This is the Pretty Derby I wanted to see!
"The day after watching the race with Tazuna-san..."
"This is the Uma Musume Training Institution."
She was there, she was there.
Eh? Did she appear in the anime?
"With the arrival of a promising Trainer,"

Eh, should I pick a Trainer-like name?
I'll be called by this, right?

Oh, that's different? Ah, it's different.

Oh crap, what should I name my Trainer Team?

Crap, that means my destined Training Uma Musume!
"Now, let's pull the Pretty Derby Gacha."
Well, honestly, if it's "Pretty," anything goes.
Alriiiight! I remember! I remember! I remember!

Ah, eh, is she the girl who came out all at once?
Like, didn't she teach me something?
Eh? Should I go to the local tracks?

Eh, she's cute but who? Not a horse.
"Let's go start your days with your assigned Uma Musume."

"From Home, you can access various places in Tracen Academy."
"You can start training your assigned Uma Musume from here."
"In order to know the Uma Musume better,"
"Playing the newly established URA Finals is recommended."

"You will experience various dramas as a Trainer."

Oh crap, my favorite Uma Musume...
There's someone I haven't seen before.
It's gotta be Daiwa Scarlet for now!
I don't know, like the Mouth of Truth or something? I don't know.
"Legend says Uma Musume are their descendants."
"They are said to be gods who always watch over and guide Uma Musume."
"Entrust their feelings before this Goddess Statue."
"The miracles run for the sake of dreams."

"The girls starting their run receive those feelings before the statue,"
"The inheritance of feelings spun continuously between Uma Musume."
"Uma Musume who entrust feelings to the Training Uma Musume are called Inheritance Uma Musume."

"By completing training and being registered as a Hall of Fame Uma Musume,"
"They can be selected as Inheritance Uma Musume."
"With the feelings held by the Inheritance Uma Musume..."
"Through Factors, you can receive benefits like base stat increases and skill hints."
"Even if selected as an inheritance source,"
"Let's select the second Inheritance Uma Musume."
There's more you have to say,
Tazuna-san, making such a cute face...
"Stats at the start of training and,"

Suzuka, Suzuka, Suzuka, Suzuka. I'll go with this!

"During training, the Support Card Bond Gauge..."

"Everyone's aspiration, the shining stage of glory."
"Let's run aiming for the Twinkle Series."
"Tazuna! As the Chairman of Tracen Academy who loves Uma Musume from the bottom of my heart, I am concerned!"
"I am extremely worried about the current situation where each individual cannot fully display their shining individuality!"
"Therefore, I propose! I will plan the holding of a new race!"
"I will create a new Grand Race!"
"A stage where every Uma Musume can shine."
"The story of you and your assigned Uma Musume begins."
Since there are many race types,
"Today again, a new Uma Musume inherits the feelings and starts running."
Eh, eh, what? What? What? What? What? What is this? What is this?
My heart kinda skipped a beat!
I've never seen such a meek Gold Ship face before.
It turned into such an amazing face!
Holy crap, it went up by 4!?
I don't know, but plus 4 feels huge numerically.
Crap, it went up too much! Factors are super important!
Whoa... Stamina Cap 4, Stamina 5, Power Cap 8.
This is crazy! Power 10! Factors are crazy!
Whoa, the caps increasing is crazy.
"The days with Daiwa Scarlet have begun."
"These are the commands for proceeding with training."

When in Rome, do as the Romans do.

As expected, my Daiwa Scarlet is #1 Favorite.

"She is the Uma Musume I expect the most from!"

"Spurt from here! The race moves at once!"
Getting passed! Getting passed! Getting passed!
Go! Go! Bad bad bad bad!

then suddenly looked like I was losing and panicked!

but was I this captivated, Subaru?
"During training, aim to achieve the goal,"
